title: Palestine Unemployed Persons
description: The number of unemployed persons in Palestine increased to 378200 in the third quarter of 2022 from 357100 in the second quarter of 2022. Unemployed Persons in Palestine averaged 327144.68  from 2010 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 445800  in the third quarter of 2018 and a record low of 195500  in the second quarter of 2011. This page provides - Palestine Unemployed Persons- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Palestinian Central Bureau of Statistics
